</section> <section class="funding-section">
    <div class="funding-container">
        
        <div class="funding-intro">
            <h2>WHY WE NEED YOUR SUPPORT</h2>
            <p>
                To compete at the highest national levels and transition our prototypes into 
                industrial-grade solutions, we require consistent backing. In the past, insufficient 
                funding forced us to pause highly promising projects like our BAJA ATV after completing 
                70% of the design phase. We are actively seeking financial and resource partners to 
                overcome these barriers and push the boundaries of student-led R&D.
            </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="grid-title">WHERE YOUR FUNDING GOES</h2>
        <div class="funding-grid">
            
            <div class="funding-card">
                <h3> Equipment & Tooling</h3>
                <p>Essential lab equipment, including precision soldering stations and heavy-duty power tools required to safely assemble complex robotic chassis.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="funding-card">
                <h3> Advanced Manufacturing</h3>
                <p>Investment in in-house 3D Printers (like the Bambu Lab A1) for rapid prototyping, reducing vendor dependency, and meeting strict competition deadlines.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="funding-card">
                <h3> Custom Electronics & Avionics</h3>
                <p>Procurement of high-performance flight controllers, custom-printed circuit boards (PCBs), and advanced sensors essential for our autonomous systems.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="funding-card">
                <h3>Overcoming Constraints</h3>
                <p>From machining custom parts manually with angle grinders to operating out of hostel rooms, our resilience is our biggest asset. Your sponsorship directly removes these bottlenecks.</p>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>
</section>

